languages.text: "А вот и... Да. Трон побери, ты права. Вы — психи, ищущие смерти, вот что я могу вам сказать!"

languages.text: 「それについては…あなたは正しい。残念だがあなたは正しい。しかし、あなたたちは二人とも、自分の死が目当てのサイコパスだ！」
languages.original_text: "Oh, I don't know about... No, you're right. Throne damn it, you're right. You're both psychopaths looking for your own death, that's all I have to say!"

languages.text: “噢，我可说不好……不，你说得对。见鬼的黄金王座，你说得对。你们两个都是自寻死路的神经病，我只想说这些！”
languages.original_text: "Oh, I don't know about... No, you're right. Throne damn it, you're right. You're both psychopaths looking for your own death, that's all I have to say!"

languages.text: "Oh, ich weiß nicht ... Nein, Ihr habt recht. Zum Thron damit, Ihr habt recht. Ihr seid beide Psychopathen, die den eigenen Tod herbeisehnen, mehr sage ich nicht!"
languages.original_text: "Oh, I don't know about... No, you're right. Throne damn it, you're right. You're both psychopaths looking for your own death, that's all I have to say!"

languages.text: « Oh, je ne sais pas si... Non, tout bien réfléchi, vous avez parfaitement raison. Le Trône m'en est témoin, vous êtes deux psychopathes qui passez votre temps à courir au-devant de la mort, et c'est tout ce que j'ai à dire ! »
languages.original_text: "Oh, I don't know about... No, you're right. Throne damn it, you're right. You're both psychopaths looking for your own death, that's all I have to say!"
